  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Herbal Supplements in Prediabetic and Mild to Moderate Hyperlipidemic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of Herbal Supplements (SR-L-01, SR-B-01 and SI-S-01) in the Management of Prediabetes and Mild to Moderate Hyperlipidemia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
