  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Objective of this study is to determine the safety and efficacy of administration of herbal
      supplements (Salacia leaf extract, Salacia root extract and Sesame seed extract) for 6 weeks
      in the management of prediabetes and mild to moderate hyperlipidemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
